marli's comments page 4
Having said all that, I'm an average middleclass woman and I feel perfectly safe. I do go out alone at night downtown, because it's always well lit, people are usually still strolling about, and there are security staff on bikes. I'm not stupid, though, and I won't park my car very far and only use welllit and secured parking lots.
